Question: Each image shows a saxophone with a curved bell in a metallic color, and the keys of each saxophone are the same color as the rest of the instrument.

Reference Answer: True

Original program:

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Does the image show a saxophone with a curved bell in a metallic color?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Does the image show a saxophone with a curved bell in a metallic color?')
ANSWER2=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Are the keys of the saxophone the same color as the rest of the instrument?')
ANSWER3=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Are the keys of the saxophone the same color as the rest of the instrument?')
ANSWER4=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} and {ANSWER2}')
ANSWER5=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER1} and {ANSWER3}')
ANSWER6=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER4} and {ANSWER5}')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER6)
```
